pageContext.claim: “The Failing New York Times wrote a story that made it seem like the White House Counsel had TURNED on the President, when in fact it is just the opposite - & the two Fake reporters knew this. This is why the Fake News Media has become the Enemy of the People. So bad for America!”
pageContext.analysis: It's unclear what the White House Counsel did or did not tell Mueller's office. The New York Times {reported} he provided 30 hours of testimony. It's unusual for a lawyer to share this much with investigators looking at his client.
